{"tid":586444,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla司機疑油門當腳掣 過路男捱撞重創","createTime":"2018-03-09T13:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T10:38:49.000Z","uid":78632,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"171599e7b46bd69c33c64f79e4da68cb0dc5589d","tid":586444,"uid":78632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:45:37.000Z","msg":"【蘋民直擊】Tesla司機疑油門當腳掣 過路男捱撞重創<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180309&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57926248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57926248&d=cPUuASb54NjB%2BpfASYGOkZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=774b8cc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180309%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57926248&h=eb4aef6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180309&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57926248</a><br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣時代廣場外發生車禍！晚上8時許，一輛Tesla私家車由停車場駛出時，撞到一名男途人。目擊者何小姐形容，當時私家車直撞該名男途人，由停車場出口衝過兩條行車線，撼向橋底石壆；懷疑是司機油門當煞掣肇禍。事後男途人昏迷由救護車送院，而私家車上女乘客亦不適送院。<br />\n何小姐當時在附近等候過路，她看到涉事Tesla私家車車上有一對夫婦，由丈夫駕車，太太則坐在其身旁座位。事發時Tesla由時代廣場的停車場駛出，剛巧一名男途人經過停車場口，Tesla撞向男途人，繼而衝過兩條行車線，撼向鵝頸橋天橋底並剷上石壆始停下。Tesla更一度冒出白煙。<br />\n何小姐直指：「嚇親囉，直情係天降橫禍，邊會諗得到行行下，都會俾架車撞親！」她更指男途人被撞到後「成面血，無晒反應！」"},{"pid":"6a0905fe6f9542d70545b01d5ad9159f21d8262d","tid":586444,"uid":12772,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:48:57.000Z","msg":"拎去打ba la"},{"pid":"e19c032fe23a239315dce658d20a4a6525311de9","tid":586444,"uid":175004,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"又香港腳發作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ee107abe7a1bde9d945e26d2d9449239848bb88","tid":586444,"uid":53441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T14:14:18.000Z","msg":"又係T"},{"pid":"f027515ae05617fc00e06a7707d13e7851b7ae35","tid":586444,"uid":126841,"like":1,"dislike":145,"score":-14